ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Granting the Transfer of Administration and Control of the Hamlet of Pond Inlet, Nunavut
PrecisOrder granting the TRANSFER OF ADMINISTRATION AND CONTROL of the federally-owned seabed located in the vicinity of the Hamlet of Pond Inlet, Nunavut, to the COMMISSIONER OF NUNAVUT in order to allow the Government of Nunavut to operate, maintain and upgrade the small craft harbour, wharf and breakwater structures according to its priorities.
